                                <div class="process-item-step-title">Нанесение клеевого состава</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="process-item process-item--3 col-12">
                        <div class="process-item-content">
                            <a class="process-item-image" href="./images/process-3.jpg" data-fancybox="process">
                                <img src="./images/process-3.jpg" alt="">
                            </a>
                            <div class="process-item-step">
                                <div class="text-outline">03</div>
                                <div class="process-item-step-title">Профилирование металла</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="process-item process-item--5 col-12">
                        <div class="process-item-content">
                            <a class="process-item-image" href="./images/process-5.jpg" data-fancybox="process">
                                <img src="./images/process-5.jpg" alt="">
                            </a>
                            <div class="process-item-step">
                                <div class="text-outline">05</div>
                                <div class="process-item-step-title">Подача PIR-компонентов</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="row">
                    <div class="process-item process-item--6 col-12">
                        <div class="process-item-content">
                            <a class="process-item-image" href="./images/process-6.jpg" data-fancybox="process">
                                <img src="./images/process-6.jpg" alt="">
                            </a>
                            <div class="process-item-step">
                                <div class="text-outline">06</div>
                                <div class="process-item-step-title">Сопряжение сердечника <br>с&nbsp;облицовками металла <br>посредством пресс-<br>термического воздействия
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="process-item process-item--7 col-12">
                        <div class="process-item-content">
                            <a class="process-item-image" href="./images/process-7.jpg" data-fancybox="process">
                                <img src="./images/process-7.jpg" alt="">
                            </a>
                            <div class="process-item-step">
                                <div class="text-outline">07</div>
                                <div class="process-item-step-title">Нарезка сэндвич-панели <br>по заданным длинам</div>
